## Summary
This documentation page describes the integration between Amplitude and Statsig for cohort synchronization, allowing users to target Statsig experiments at specific cohorts created in Amplitude, with setup instructions for both platforms and steps for sending cohorts that will appear under Segments in Statsig within 15 minutes.

